title: Talented GIF-makers
body: Now that the whole season is out, if anyone wants to make a gif set of all the times Lucas made the “Please kiss me”-face, and also one with all the times Lucas looked blissed out/love drunk I’d be eternally greatful. Our angry hedgehog was such a soft boy and those where some of his most endearing moments that continued throughout the entire season imo. It would be so funny and cute to see them all in one place.
